What Makes Deployment Special:
The Deployment automatically:

ðŸ”„ Keeps 1 pizza ready at all times (if someone eats it, makes a new one)

ðŸ“ˆ Can easily scale to 5 pizzas (just change replicas: 5)

ðŸ”„ Can upgrade to new recipe without stopping the pizza service

